headline: 3 Stocks to Buy for “Liberation Day 2.0”
summary: For better or worse, April’s “Liberation Day” was a chance to make a lot of money. On the positive side, the volatility surge created some incredible deals. In mid-April, I reported how one of our quant systems identified five incredible stocks to buy during this period. Here’s how they’ve done since: InvestorPlace - Stock Market News, Stock Advice & Trading Tips Papa John’s International Inc. (PZZA): +29% Coupang Inc. (CPNG): +26% JBT Marel Corp. (JBTM): +18% Dollar General Corp. (DG): +14% Spa
